<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Medical vocabulary is a goldmine for Scrabble players. These words often use unusual letter combinations (ZY, PH, XY) that score well and confuse opponents who might challenge perfectly valid terms. From anatomy to pharmacology, here are the medical words worth knowing.</p>

<p>Healthcare professionals have a natural advantage in Scrabble — their everyday vocabulary includes hundreds of valid words that casual players have never encountered. Even if you're not in medicine, learning these terms adds powerful weapons to your arsenal.</p>

